token_info.name: ENGAGE TRIANGLE METAMORPH #1
token_info.description: An early Blender sculpt from my painting "ENGAGE TRIANGLE", suspended and morphing. It can be physically produced on a 3D printer, either at an animation frame of your choosing or one chosen randomly by me - to enable this after purchase, please contact jon@wilyguys.com for a file optimised for 3D printers.
